import React from "react";
import { Button, Card, CardBody, CardText, CardTitle, Container } from "reactstrap";

const Course = () => {
    return <>
        <Card>
            <CardBody>
                <CardTitle style={{fontSize:'large'}}>java tutorials</CardTitle>
                <CardText>this tutorails for biginer , every body can undrstnad this coueses</CardText>
                <Container className="text-center">
                    <Button color='danger'>Delete</Button>
                    <Button color='warning' style={{marginLeft:'10px'}}>Update</Button>
                </Container>
            </CardBody>
        </Card>
    </>
}
export default Course;
